description: The first chapter of a six-part story arc, featuring the stunning debut of new regular artist Mike Deodato Jr. (INCREDIBLE HULK) and the introduction of two new characters that will be discussed for years to come!Mary Jane auditions for the play "Cats Always Lie". The director gives her some advice,and the part. Peter and MJ celebrates in Forest Hills with May until a letter arrives from Gwen Stacy. Reading it Peter learns that Gwen had some bad news, but half the message is missing. MJ wonders how long the letter must have been. lost in the mail system but Peter points out the postage is only from days ago. Peter visits Gwen's grave where he is taunted by two mysterious attackers. He fights them off and escapes by sticking to a passing truck. The attackers realize that Peter is Spider-Man.
name: Sins Past Part One
The Wrath of Kings

description: Part two continues as Banzai, along with his Hong Kong Cavaliers, protects our way of life as we know it! Meanwhile they must contend with: remembering where they parked the Jet Car, a huge elector-magnetic pulse, the Widows buttocks, Lectroids, a misplaced syringe, and the World Crime League! Gah! Who has time for a "sound check" at this rate! The rollicking adventure picks up steam as the crap really hits the fan in this one!

volume.name: Buckaroo Banzai: Return of the Screw

description: Part 3 of this rollicking saga concludes as Banzai, along with his Hong Kong Cavaliers, think outside of the box to make sure our world can safely go to sleep at night!Hearts are broken, a birth of something strange, a photo with a sad memory, a road trip with Uzis, the Man in the Moon, an assault on a Lectroid stronghold, Tommy as Tarzan, unerring marksmanship, the taste of a good rope, and all that wrapped inside a riddle about an elephant! But when will they have the time to book the studio to record their next smash album?

volume.name: Buckaroo Banzai: Return of the Screw
Buckaroo Banzai: Return of the Screw Preview

3000 years after releasing monsters from another dimension an immortal warrior king waits for the stars to align and the chance to redeem himself.

The Haunted Pizza Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Special

description: Paul finally returns to his native Japan. He finds that the "golden age" of monsters has fallen on hard times. There he meets Gomorra a legendary monster in his own right! The town fathers are trying to get Gomorra back into fighting trim and to generate tourism and business!
name: Paul vs. Gomorra

description: This the third in the three-comic 'mini-series' of the official 'Encyclopedia' to the Tick Universe. Each issue features 1 to 3-page long write-ups about various important characters who have appeared in Tick and Tick-related comics. Issue 3 covers events that happened after the 1&2 were published.
name: 1993 Update

volume.name: The Tick's Giant Circus of the Mighty

description: Heather has been kidnapped... and the Crime Cannibal has gone ballistic trying to find her!
name: Hunting Heather

description: This issue is part 2 of the "Crisis on Finite Tick Spin-Offs"! The Tick's ONLY crossover story. Thrill to the action as The Tick - Cow; Paul and various other super-heroes confront a galaxy of super-bad-guys who are in league with none other than the resurrected Sagin the Wolf! Sagin strikes with full force using ninjas; the Miti Men and ruthlessness to subdue our valiant warrior from quelling his evil rampage!
name: Rising Sagin

description:
This issue is part 4 of the "Crisis on Finite Tick Spin-Offs"! The Tick's ONLY crossover story. Thrill to the action as The Tick; Cow; Paul and various other super-heroes confront a galaxy of super-bad-guys who are in league with none other than the resurrected Sagin the Wolf!

Has Paul joined forces with none other than Sagin? Does this spell the end of all that is good and just? Find out; get this book!
name: Lo, a Cow Shall Lead Them!

description: A classic contribution to American popular culture, Little Lulu is the ultimate all-ages comic! The humor is quick-witted and fresh, the characters are unique and delightful, and the art is simply out of this world. Join Lulu, Tubby, Annie, Iggy, and all the rest of the troublemaking gang as they get themselves into some seriously silly situations. Lulu outwits the clubhouse boys, tells tales of the wicked Witch Hazel, and even solves a few mysteries with help from The Spider (AKA Tubby) in this fun-filled volume. John Stanley and Irving Tripp were master craftsmen of comedy and the world they brought to life is timeless. Adults and children alike are sure to love these hilarious stories of one clever little girl and her legion of lovable pals.
name: Handy Kid

description:
Well before the Brothers War, on the world of Dominaria, the continent of Corondor is spanned by warring peoples. Life has come to have little value to both the draconian city-states and primitive clans living there.

However, in this darkest of times, an improbable soul rises to meet the need of the land. Legends are made.
name: Dakkon Blackblade

volume.name: Dakkon Blackblade: A Magic the Gathering Legend

description: Caliphear is unsummoned back to the world Dominaria to find that all is not right. After battling an Azure Drake, she discovers her home ravaged with most lying dead. A question remains. "Who did this...?"
name: Nightmare: Vanishing Lands

description: This tale is set on the continent of Corondor of the world Dominaria. It begins with a clash on the plains of Golthonor and escalates with the introduction of Serra Angels. Legends grow from the conflict that ensues.
name: Fallen Angel

volume.name: Fallen Angel: A Magic the Gathering Legend

description: Dead and buried.

In the 31st century, three teens from different worlds act to save prominent businessman R.J. Brande from assassination. Their courageous act will change their lives forever and tie them to a conspiracy threatening the fragile foundations of the burgeoning United Planets. Definitive Legion writer Paul Levitz teams up with Chris Batista to explore what exactly distinguishes the Legionnaires from the other super-powered members of their respective races.
name: Target
